author: alexdma
msg: - Fixed a bug in ONManagerImpl that caused the ontology storage to be passed as an argument before being instantiated. This bug arose when creating non-OSGi constructors and activators for all service implementations.
- Renamed OntologyStorage to ClerezzaOntologyStorage, moved to ontologymanager.ontonet.io and refactored references.
- Created InMemoryOntologyStorage as a fallback for missing Clerezza storage (e.g. when not supplied in non-OSGi environments)
- Added org.apache.clerezza.rdf.jena.parser as a dependency for reengineer/db and reengineer/xml (TODO: unit tests could be performed in-memory though).
